.TH "pvrdma_query_port" 9 "pvrdma_query_port" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pvrdma_query_port \- query device port attributes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pvrdma_query_port
.BI "(struct ib_device *ibdev "  ","
.BI "u8 port "  ","
.BI "struct ib_port_attr *props "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ibdev" 12
the device to query
.IP "port" 12
the port number
.IP "props" 12
the device properties
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, otherwise negative errno
